column2: "Oh, hello there. You feel it don't you, this feeling of Darkers?"
"Today, it feels especially strong even though there aren't very many of them around."
"Seems wrong, it seems so wrong. Why is there air this thick when there's nothing here?"
"Further in? Further down? I wonder how far we need to go to find it?"
"That's fine. It doesn't really matter, we just need to kill them all."
"It's fun isn't it? Just massacring Darkers, right?"
"第1章 受け継がれぬ遺志"
